{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r715084928", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great experience beyond food", "diner_date": " October 2019", "rating_date": "3 October 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "James X", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r715084928-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["It\u2019s the first time after having starter, I look forward to the main course. The food was so good that I kept feeling like it\u2019s a flavour experience. The knowledge from Gerson and the friendliness from Giorgio made us feel really relaxed and cheerful. The environment was perfect and relaxing. The views was also part of the experience. I think it\u2019s my top restaurant for local and modern cuisine. Really really good. Worth checking it out!"]}
