{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r711457852", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "A pleasure for the senses", "diner_date": " September 2019", "rating_date": "20 September 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "privacyissues", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r711457852-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["One of the best dining experiences in London so far. I was advised to try the tasting menu, luckily i did, it was amazing, the wine paired exquisitely. The manager Marco and the staff were very professional and polite, it was a pleasure interfacing with them. I loved the food as much as the view, Canary Wharf looking splendid from the restaurant. An absolute must, recommended, can't wait to be back!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r711430730", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Not enough superlatives...", "diner_date": " September 2019", "rating_date": "20 September 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "MarkCDesmond", "reviewer_origin": ["Greater London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "10"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "10"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r711430730-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I have to be honest from the outset - we\u2019ve visited Peninsula a number of times and have been fans of this restaurant for a while.", "The food is consistently high quality and occasionally inventive. The venue itself is a little \u2018corporate\u2019 but the setting is beautiful and with a wonderful view of the Thames, nighttime dining is something quite special.", "The wine list is extensive and well managed.", "The reason for posting a review after so many previous visits is the recent changes in personnel. Whilst the staff have always been impressive. with their discrete attentiveness and knowledgeable of the menu, their willingness to engage and make recommendations of well placed wine pairings, together with background knowledge of menu items, had elevated eating here from a solid dining experience to a sublime gastronomic one.", "As an interested self-confessed foodie, it\u2019s a pleasure to find waiting staff as interested in the food and wine as I am, and their willingness to engage with diners on the topics is both welcome and refreshing.", "On this basis, our occasional visits to Penisula will now become frequent and regular.", "Kudos to the management team for putting together, training, and fostering a team that can present and elevate the menu to such a high engaging standard.", "I\u2019ve run out of superlatives!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r708434664", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Tasting menu dinner", "diner_date": " September 2019", "rating_date": "10 September 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "SarahNB123", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "8"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r708434664-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["The two of us went one evening for the 7 course tasting menu dinner. We had a voucher from Virgin Experiences. We also opted for the wine pairing which was an additional cost. Every course was delicious and very well presented. The service was excellent and our table had a great view of Canary Wharf by the window. Would highly recommend."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r710920394", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "One of the best menus I\u2019ve tasted in London", "diner_date": " September 2019", "rating_date": "18 September 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "H8801JLriccardor", "reviewer_origin": ["Parma, Italy"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r710920394-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I had a wonderful experience at the peninsula restaurant while visiting friends in East London. ", "First and foremost: absolutely outstanding service. ", "Our Italian waiter Giorgio delivered an exceptional guidance towards choosing the best wine for our 7 course menu, which has been one of the finest dining experience I\u2019ve had in London this year. ", "The French-inspired menu \u00e1 la Pierre Gagnaire was a true voyage that can be enjoyed better with those dear to you, for how heartwarming it is.", "Every dish perfectly executed and all in a relaxing, intimate dining situation, with a jaw-dropping view of Canada Water.", "Will come again and again. I think my girlfriend will love this place. "]}
