{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r651825560", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Private dining - perfect for small party", "diner_date": " March 2018", "rating_date": "12 February 2019", "answer_text": ["Dear ktee78", "Thank you for taking the time to write to us about your recent dining experience in our restaurant. Both our front of house and kitchen brigade are grateful for the kind words. We look forward to welcoming you back in the very near future.", "Kind regards,", "Domenico Pizzo", "Restaurant Manager at Peninsula restaurant "], "reviewer_pseudo": "kateoben78", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "11"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r651825560-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Been a few times. With a larger group when we booked the private dining room and in small groups at the main restaurant. Food excellent. Presentation amazing!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r640894808", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Perfect.", "diner_date": " December 2018", "rating_date": "21 December 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear t0mmyangles", "Thank you for your review regarding your visit to Peninsula Restaurant.", "We really appreciate you taking the time to share your experience with us. We count ourselves lucky for customers like you and we look forward welcoming you again in the future.", "Best regards,", "Domenico Pizzo", "Restaurant Manager at Peninsula restaurant"], "reviewer_pseudo": "t0mmyangles", "reviewer_origin": ["Redhill, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r640894808-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We were a party of 7 with 3 children. 5 of us had the seven course tasting menu, 3 guests with accompanying wine. It\u2019s difficult to explain how good this restaurant is so I\u2019ll try to break it down. ", "The food: Fine dining at its best. The flavours, textures and contrasts were spot on, exquisitely presented. The Wagyu beef course being my favourite. The chef made our youngest guests some pasta with sauce and cheese which was also delicious.", "The service: Professional and warm. Our sommelier Olga was highly informed.", "The view: Amazing. If you went to impress someone, take them here! ", "Thank you Peninsula, a perfect night x"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r642898388", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "NYE tasting menus", "diner_date": " January 2019", "rating_date": "1 January 2019", "answer_text": ["Dear DIana S", "Thank you for taking the time to write to us about your recent dining experience in our restaurant. Both our front of house and kitchen brigade are grateful for the kind words. We look forward to welcoming you back in the very near future.", "Kind regards,", "Domenico Pizzo", "Restaurant Manager at Peninsula restaurant "], "reviewer_pseudo": "Diana S", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "110"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "29"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r642898388-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We had a 7 course tasting menu on NYE, and there were two additional surprise courses. \u00a395pp was a very reasonable price for NYE (Wagamama on Southbank was charging \u00a3160pp for a three courses & access to the terrace to see the fireworks...phhhh).", "Back to the Peninsula menu:", "- bread & butter - nice", "- pre-starter of cauliflower and Brussels sprouts - nice, interesting presentation", "- beetroot starter - beautiful presentation, very delicate, but the taste was a bit too simple", "- lobster in bisque - this had a very strong fish smell, which I didn't like and it was too salty for me. Lobster, however, was well cooked and wasn't dry or rubbery", "- foie gras - whipped & very buttery. Beautifully presented. I would've liked a toasted warm brioch on a side as the foie gras was very rich.", "- turbot - well cooked, but nothing special", "- beef - this was an A1 wagyu filet and it was absolutely devine!", "- cheese - this was a very unusual dish, more like a soup. Fantastic textures, but it was way too salty for me. My boyfriend loved it though.", "- surprise pre-dessert - apple & sorrel ice cream with meringue - perfection in terms of taste, texture & presentation", "- milk chocolate dessert - again absolutely perfection!", "I didn't love all the dishes, but I would definitely like to go back and try other options from the a la cart menu next time.", "The restaurant is lovely with panoramic windows looking at the skyscrapers in Canary Wharf. The waiters are very knowledgeable, friendly and polite."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r649666608", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing Dinner. ", "diner_date": " February 2019", "rating_date": "2 February 2019", "answer_text": ["Dear Stelian89", "Thank you for choosing to dine with us at Peninsula Restaurant; It is an absolute pleasure to read your review. We are so pleased that you found our restaurant welcoming and that you enjoyed both the food and service. Our staff genuinely cares very deeply about each and every guest and strive to provide the best customer experience to all. ", "Thank you once again for the great comments and we really hope you will decide to visit us again in the near future.", "Warm regards,", "Peninsula Restaurant Team"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Stelian89", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r649666608-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I've been to Peninsula Restaurant with 6 other friends for my birthday dinner. We had a fantastic evening. We've been welcomed at the door by the Manager who also organised a lovely table by the window for us. We choose the 7 course tasting menu which exeed our expectations. Every course was wonderfully presented and very delicious! ", "Our experience was complimented by a flawless service from Khadija! Thank you, Khadija, thank you Peninsula! I will definitely go back! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r642069291", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Worst Taste I have ever Experienced ", "diner_date": " December 2018", "rating_date": "28 December 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear moreuknow", "Thank you for taking the time to share about your recent dinner at Peninsula restaurant. Your feedback and comments are extremely valuable to us and we have taken them on-board as we aim to go above and beyond for our guests at all times. Please be assured that we have addressed all the matters raised in your review with the team involved, who join me in regretting the obvious disappointment caused to you on the day and the impact it had on what should have been a very special occasion. I would like to discuss the points raised further with you personally if you would be so kind as to: contact me on peninsularestaurant@iclondontheo2.com ", "With kindest regards,", "Domenico Pizzo", "Restaurant Manager at Peninsula restaurant"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Minoolifediaryinsta", "reviewer_origin": ["Los Angeles, California"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "50"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "33"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r642069291-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["This is the Michelin Resturant. However, I gave this one star because it totally disappointed me for fine dinning experience on food taste although the environment and staff both were fabulous during our visit. We have ordered the 7 course experience which was most expensive (75\u00a3 per person). Pros: The bread and initial setup was tasty. And first appetizer was delicious ( Pumpkin Thai) with vey nice set up. The Octopus was also delicious with great presentation. Cons: but disappointments starts from 3rd appetizers and entries. BBQ prawn was almost raw and taste awful. The duck liver !!!! Taste so bad that I almost drink whole bottle of water to get rid of taste in my mouth. The Wagyu beef was also served raw with very disappointing presentation and taste so bad. These are their main entries not only taste bad, but also presented poorly. The dessert is also very very regular chocolate desert with nothing special, you can find similar taste in small cafe shop. This is my personal experience."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r640299105", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing experience!", "diner_date": " December 2018", "rating_date": "18 December 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear ledianiko", "Thank you for choosing to dine with us at Peninsula Restaurant; It is an absolute pleasure to read your review. We are so pleased that you found our restaurant welcoming and that you enjoyed both the food and service. Our staff genuinely cares very deeply about each and every guest and strive to provide the best customer experience to all. ", "Thank you once again for the great comments and we really hope you will decide to visit us again in the near future.", "Warm regards,", "Peninsula Restaurant Team"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Ledia N", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r640299105-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I do not frequently write reviews by my friends and I had such an amazing evening at the Peninsula so I feel inclined to share. The restaurant itself is beautifully designed and has a great ambience, accentuated by the wonderful view of London. The food presentation was immaculate and every dish was delicious. We all went for the 7-course tasting menu and I particularly enjoyed the Foie Grass and the Wagyu Beef dishes. ", "The staff were charming, friendly and helpful, all working hard to make it a memorable occasion for us. We especially enjoyed talking to Hermes, who was so lovely and attentive. He went out of his way to make us feel comfortable and did an amazing job at explaining each dish. ", "I would definitely recommend and I look forward to returning. ", "P.S. If you have time for a drink after dinner, I would recommend going to Sky Bar- lovely staff and stunning views."]}
