{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r634173675", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Beautiful!", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "18 November 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Amy W,", "Thank you very much for your review. We are thrilled to see you enjoyed the views and had a good experience dining at Peninsula Restaurant. ", "We will be delighted to pass on your lovely feedback about our Chef and Colleagues who will be equally as pleased to hear such a fantastic review as they go above and beyond everyday to ensure all our guests experience only the best service. ", "Thank you once again for the lovely feedback and we are looking forward to welcoming you again", "Warm regards,", "Peninsula Restaurant Team"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Amy W", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r634173675-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We had the five course tasting menu and it was superb. Excellent service and gorgeous views across Canary Wharf. Can\u2019t fault it!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r639011167", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "View, Service and Food A+", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "11 December 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Bmama88", "Thank you for your review regarding your visit to Peninsula Restaurant.", "We really appreciate you taking the time to share your experience with us. We count ourselves lucky for customers like you and we look forward welcoming you again in the future.", "Best regards,", "Domenico Pizzo", "Restaurant Manager at Peninsula restaurant"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Bmama88", "reviewer_origin": ["Diamond Bar, California"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "14"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "35"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r639011167-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["This is such a well balance restaurant that gives you that intimate feel, as well as great views. Our family of 5 from Seniors to Teenagers enjoyed the meal without staffs \" rolling eyes\" like some high end restaurants. All us had the Chef tasting menu, Interesting selections on the ingredient used, but great presentation. Few dishes were predictable but overall is a great place to bring date or family. Our tabs came around $500+`- but its a decent price tag considering how expensive London meal price is. Only down side was this is located far from City center..took us 1 hour and 25 min to get there....."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r633831364", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Beautiful solo meal & send-off", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "16 November 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear DaniMarissa", "Thank you for your review regarding your visit to Peninsula Restaurant.", "We really appreciate you taking the time to share your experience with us. We count ourselves lucky for customers like you and we look forward welcoming you again in the future.", "Best regards,", "Domenico Pizzo", "Restaurant Manager at Peninsula restaurant"], "reviewer_pseudo": "DaniMarissa", "reviewer_origin": ["Towaco, New Jersey"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "7"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r633831364-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I chose to treat myself on my last night in London on 11/10/18 during my first ever solo trip. After hours of research, I decided to make my reservation at The Peninsula online. I asked, with no expectations, if they would possibly spare a table by the window so that I could have the stunning view for my last night there. Again, no expectations on my part and I didn't expect them to waste a great table on one person! Upon arrival, I was greeted and taken to my incredible table - in the corner, right at the window where I was told \"as requested.\" That alone meant so very much to me. Olga immediately came over to greet me and take my drink order and make me feel 100% comfortable - being alone was totally new to me but she made me completely relaxed and offered help or information whenever needed about the menu. I decided to go for the 7 course (why not!) and let me tell you, TREAT YOURSELF!!!! The chef is far too talented and the food is too exquisite to pass up every offering. No matter how full you are, keep eating. It's worth every bite. And the bread...it's what dreams are made of! The manager Domenico was so kind to me and made me feel like I was the only person in the whole restaurant - I was treated like an absolute queen. Chef Tomas even came out to bring a main course! From top to bottom, beginning to end, the meal was absolutely sublime. Each course was a textural symphony and the foie gras with a salted pancake? LIFE CHANGING. The creativity and thoughtfulness seen in each dish was phenomenal and every course kept getting more and more fabulous. The dessert was something I have been thinking about since I left! The banana tiramisu is just fantastic. Plus, the view was to die for. I've never had a dinner where so many different textures were evident and everything was so perfectly balanced between salty, sweet, sour, crunchy, and creamy. I could not have imagined a better way to spend my last night in London - a stunning view, a gorgeous dinner, and the best treatment I've ever received in a restaurant (I even got a surprise of a signed menu form Chef Tomas, how cool is that?!). There is no restaurant more deserving of a Michelin star. My heartfelt, never ending thanks to Domenico, Olga, Chef Tomas & the kitchen staff for giving me a beautiful experience and memory to last a lifetime. I am truly grateful and hope to someday head back to the Peninsula again."]}
