{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r633143077", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Anniversary dinner", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "13 November 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear CAmzn,", "Thank you for your review regarding your visit in Peninsula restaurant ", "I was most concerned to read that you were disappointed with our food selection. Please rest assured that your comments have been discussed with my team,", "and accept my sincerest apologies for any shortcomings. I would very much welcome the opportunity to discuss your experience in more detail and should you want to do so I may be contacted at peninsularestaurant@iclondontheo2.com ", "I look forward to hearing from you. ", "Best regards,", "Domenico Pizzo", "Restaurant Manager at Peninsula restaurant"], "reviewer_pseudo": "CAmzn", "reviewer_origin": ["England, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "127"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "157"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r633143077-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Ongoing building works outside aside, the Peninsula has everything going for it. The location is fantastic, the views are lovely and the atmosphere inside the restaurant is delightful, possibly because it was mostly empty for the duration of our meal. We used a voucher from Virgin but genuinely felt that the pricing was reasonable without it. Booking was difficult- for whatever reason there are a lot of phone agents that are hard to understand handling that side of things. At first we couldn't get through at all. We were eventually told to call later in the week because there was a convention at the hotel. It wasn't the best customer service that we've encountered, certainly.", "I was able to make a substitution which I did appreciate, and I also loved how painstakingly each dish in our seven course menu was plated. I suppose that I just feel style is no substitute for substance, which was lacking. We grew tired of each dish being drowned in au jus or sauce until every bite was a wet mess instead of leaving more textures in play. Tender I can appreciate, but the softness of every dish, being whipped or pureed made me feel like the menu is catered to a much, much older patron. Enjoying the foie gras, I had hardly enough time to appreciate the attention to detail before our waitress returned- she had forgotten yet another jus and on it went. Our \"cheese course\" was a single mozzarella stick served with honey olive oil and another dip. Having read great things about the cheeses on offer in the restaurant, I could only laugh. Hoping to end on a high we awaited our dessert which was unfortunately just another pretty but ultimately soft and bland banana pudding. I waited all evening for something that I could really get my teeth into but it never arrived. It's possible we just chose a less thrilling taster menu night, but for an occasion it was very disappointing."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r624780917", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Outstanding ", "diner_date": " October 2018", "rating_date": "14 October 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Chris M,", "Thank you for choosing to dine with us at Peninsula Restaurant; It is an absolute pleasure to read your review. We are so pleased that you found our restaurant welcoming and that you enjoyed both the food and service. Our staff genuinely cares very deeply about each and every guest and strive to provide the best customer experience to all. ", "Thank you once again for the great comments and we really hope you will decide to visit us again in the near future.", "Warm regards,", "Peninsula Restaurant Team"], "reviewer_pseudo": "V1263KCchrism", "reviewer_origin": ["Larkfield, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r624780917-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We visited the peninsula as we had a gift certificate including the planetarium in Greenwich. There was very limited choice through the experience but it didn\u2019t matter at all. I had food I wouldn\u2019t have usually ordered and was blown away, it was lovely. Was also given a few complimentary extras which consisted of some canopies on arrival, some freshly baked bread and an extra dessert. The views over the Thames and London was excellent. Amazing service will definitely be visiting again"]}
