{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r612840195", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Worth it! ", "diner_date": " September 2018", "rating_date": "1 September 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear LeeshaBee,", "Thank you very much for your review. We are thrilled to see you enjoyed the views and had a good experience dining at Peninsula Restaurant. ", "We will be delighted to pass on your lovely feedback about our Chef and Colleagues who will be equally as pleased to hear such a fantastic review as they go above and beyond everyday to ensure all our guests experience only the best service. ", "Thank you once again for the lovely feedback and we are looking forward to welcoming you again", "Warm regards,", "Peninsula Restaurant Team"], "reviewer_pseudo": "LeeshaBee", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "10"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "7"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r612840195-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["If you\u2019re staying nearby this is defiantly worth a visit. Great staff, even better food. Beautiful views. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r600981760", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Sigita Ta", "diner_date": " July 2018", "rating_date": "30 July 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Sigutetallat", ",", "Thank you for choosing to dine with us at Peninsula Restaurant; It is an absolute pleasure to read your review. We are so pleased that you found our restaurant welcoming and that you enjoyed both the food and service. Our staff genuinely cares very deeply about each and every guest and strive to provide the best customer experience to all. ", "Thank you once again for the great comments and we really hope you will decide to visit us again in the near future.", "Warm regards,", "Peninsula Restaurant Team"], "reviewer_pseudo": "sigutetallat", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r600981760-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We visited Peninsula Restaurant saturday evening and i must say we had absolutely wonderful evening. ", "We had tasting menu with wines pairing. Every dish was carefully crafted to perfection - like a piece of art and most importantly- delicious.My personal favourite was Highland beef with golf ball onions, miso and horseradish. ", "Our server Olga and restaurant manager (i am sorry i don't recall the name) described every course and explained why they chose the wine for it. The wine was delightful and really enhanced the flavours of this amazing food. I strongly suggest you do the wine pairing.", "All in all staff were extremely friendly, professional and attentive all night. ", "We had some dietary requirements, which were not forgotten.", "On a negative side, when we arrived at the restaurant, it was quite busy and it was a bit too hot for me inside. Also, and this is just my opinion, the interior design needs a bit of modernisation. ", "I will definitely return to Peninsula Restaurant just to taste these amazing dishes again!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r610277529", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Every plate a work of art!", "diner_date": " August 2018", "rating_date": "25 August 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Sharon b,", "Thank you very much for your review. We are thrilled to see you enjoyed the views and had a good experience dining at Peninsula Restaurant. ", "We will be delighted to pass on your lovely feedback about our Chef and Colleagues who will be equally as pleased to hear such a fantastic review as they go above and beyond everyday to ensure all our guests experience only the best service. ", "Thank you once again for the lovely feedback and we are looking forward to welcoming you again", "Warm regards,", "Peninsula Restaurant Team"], "reviewer_pseudo": "sharon b", "reviewer_origin": ["Essex, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "17"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "8"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r610277529-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We ate at this restaurant as part of a gift experience I bought for my husband for Christmas. We were a little unsure as, despite eating at plenty of fine dining restaurants, we had never experienced a tasting menu before. We were not disappointed. The food was delicious and beautifully presented. We felt a little guilty not having wine with our meal but we are not big wine drinkers and much prefer plain old water when we experience food of this quality. The waiting staff were excellent and , if anything, a little too attentive but they had an excellent knowledge of the food they were serving and were clearly very proud to be presenting it. The restaurant has a lovely outlook over the river and has a very pleasant ambience. We had an added bonus of a pre starter and some petit four at the end of our meal which, with a liqueur coffee, finished off the evening perfectly. It was a perfect treat for us and I wish we could have afforded to stay over night. Maybe next time!"]}
