{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r601532547", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Lovely treat!!!", "diner_date": " July 2018", "rating_date": "31 July 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Hann2403,", "Thank you for choosing to dine with us at Peninsula Restaurant; It is an absolute pleasure to read your review. We are so pleased that you found our restaurant welcoming and that you enjoyed both the food and service. Our staff genuinely cares very deeply about each and every guest and strive to provide the best customer experience to all. ", "Thank you once again for the great comments and we really hope you will decide to visit us again in the near future.", "Warm regards,", "Peninsula Restaurant Team"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Hann2403", "reviewer_origin": ["Melbourn, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "87"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "28"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r601532547-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Visited here on a lovely Saturday evening. From the start the service was second to none; everyone was really polite, friendly and attentive.", "Ordered from a set menu which still had plenty of choice! Enjoyed a lovely glass of prosecco to wash down the nibbles given to start off with. Then followed the homemade bread and butter was to die for and presented in a really quirky way.", "Scallops for starter were the best I\u2019ve tasted, full of flavour and looked inviting in the bowl!", "Main was even better, beautifully presented and really gave my taste buds a ride.", "Dessert finished the meal off nicely, really refreshing!", "Yes it is expensive, but personally it\u2019s worth every penny. I would go back again as a treat without a doubt."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r612969414", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fantastic", "diner_date": " September 2018", "rating_date": "1 September 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear BEEMB,", "Thank you for your review regarding your visit to Peninsula Restaurant.", "We really appreciate you taking the time to share your experience with us. We count ourselves lucky for customers like you and we look forward welcoming you again in the future.", "Best regards,", "Domenico Pizzo", "Restaurant Manager at Peninsula restaurant"], "reviewer_pseudo": "BEEMB", "reviewer_origin": ["KENT"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "44"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "12"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r612969414-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Give yourself enough time before your meal to visit the 18th floor bar for a drink or two with an impressive view. This will set you up perfectly for the delicious food that awaits with excellent service. It really should have a michelin star - each course being spot on. ", "We shall go back ! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r589115942", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "anerversary dinner", "diner_date": " June 2018", "rating_date": "20 June 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear mike j, ", "We are delighted that you chose to celebrate your anniversary celebration with us at the restaurant and thank you for your positive feedback. ", "As We sincerely value our guest\u2019s feedback and, entire team joins me in sending our heartfelt thanks. ", "I look forward to welcoming you back to enjoy future menus which evolve throughout the seasons.", "With kindest regards,", "Domenico Pizzo", "Restaurant Manager at Peninsula restaurant"], "reviewer_pseudo": "mike j", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "277"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1137"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r589115942-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["on arrival met by the hotel concierge who told us there was a skyline bar on the 18 floor so off we went wow , fantastic views of London & taken to a great window table two great cocktails and great service nuts and crisp also brought to the table as well could no fault we will return to this bar . now onto the food went down to the resturant great welcome & taken to another great table with another great view , we went for the tasteing menu with matching wines, food ,service and wine were all fantastic could not ask for more one of the better tasting menu in some time big shout out for our waitress she was supberb through out and just added to our eating expirence & like the bar we will be coming back oh a nice touch at the end with that little extra treat , many thanks guys."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r590084146", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Extraordinary", "diner_date": " June 2018", "rating_date": "23 June 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Roberts K,", "Thank you for taking the time to write to us about your recent dining experience in our restaurant. Both our front of house and kitchen brigade are grateful for the kind words. We look forward to welcoming you back in the very near future.", "Kind regards,", "Domenico Pizzo", "Restaurant Manager at Peninsula restaurant "], "reviewer_pseudo": "Roberts K", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r590084146-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Our visit was a truly incredible experience! Was really looking forward to this visit and all expectations were set pretty high, so any smallest mistake could be really disappointing, however, everything from the moment we arrived, until we left was outstanding! Staff was very professional, with high standards and at the same time very friendly! Meals (tasting menu) - I would describe it as a piece of art! Every single dish complimented and fulfilled the whole experience. All the flavors were very well paired, lots of work, passion, and creativity behind every dish. I would definitely recommend this place for fine dining, with incredible view overseeing canary wharf, great service, and extremely great meals!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r592736376", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Tasting Menu - Outstanding!", "diner_date": " July 2018", "rating_date": "3 July 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Chris W", "Thank you for your review regarding your visit to Peninsula Restaurant.", "We really appreciate you taking the time to share your experience with us. We count ourselves lucky for customers like you and we look forward welcoming you again in the future.", "Best regards,", "Domenico Pizzo", "Restaurant Manager at Peninsula restaurant"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Chris W", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r592736376-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We booked in for the tasting menu at the Peninsula restaurant and couldn't be happier with our experience! ", "The staff were wonderful, knowledgeable, and very attentive. From the time of booking to the time we left, the staff ensured we felt welcome, it was also my partner's birthday and they made sure we had a table will an amazing view of the Thames, and even brought out a surprise dessert dish with 'happy birthday!' piped across it! our waiter, Ionut, was so passionate about the food, the room, the view (and his cheeses!) which brought a smile to our faces! ", "The food on the tasting menu was magnificent! The textures, appearance, taste, and the smell of each course were some of the best we've ever had, everything complimented each other perfectly. Ionut sent our messages of thanks and praise to the Chefs, and was delighted to learn just how passionate they are about their dishes, and always striving to be better. ", "I can't recommend this place enough - book for a wonderful evening!"]}
