{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r589969212", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "A must to try!", "diner_date": " June 2018", "rating_date": "23 June 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Lina K,", "Thank you for taking the time to write to us about your recent dining experience in our restaurant. Both our front of house and kitchen brigade are grateful for the kind words. We look forward to welcoming you back in the very near future.", "Kind regards,", "Domenico Pizzo", "Restaurant Manager at Peninsula restaurant "], "reviewer_pseudo": "Lina K", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r589969212-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Second time here, first for my husband. He isn't a big fan of this type of dinners as they make him feel too unconfortable. But even him loved the food and the atmosphere! We had a tasting menu and let me tell you if you are planing on that maybe save some space in the belly during the day! The food was as delicious as it was beautiful! All the amazing plates makes it even better! The staff members were really nice, have been aproached maybe by 3-4 different ones but that did not feel annoying. With every dish there was a little introduction that made it a little more special. I prefer the view then the sun goes down, and the lights goes on. But since the food is so great and beatiful you don't really have the time or need to look around! All in all great experience, already planning another visit, and would probably try it this time with a wine pairing, as I heard it makes the experience even better! ", "Well done and keep up the good work!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r596019438", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing food and service ", "diner_date": " July 2018", "rating_date": "14 July 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Thu Ngoc H,", "Thank you very much for your review. We are thrilled to see you enjoyed the views and had a good experience dining at Peninsula Restaurant. ", "We will be delighted to pass on your lovely feedback about our Chef and Colleagues who will be equally as pleased to hear such a fantastic review as they go above and beyond everyday to ensure all our guests experience only the best service. ", "Thank you once again for the lovely feedback and we are looking forward to welcoming you again", "Warm regards,", "Peninsula Restaurant Team"], "reviewer_pseudo": "thungochoang", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r596019438-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["The food was so AMAZING that I need to leave a review, from starters to desserts me and my bf was really satisfied, every dish was made with care and passion (I love the foie gras). This is the best restaurant I\u2019ve been to for a while. The service was on point. The view was nice. I also love how it wasnt so crowded when I came. Nice and quite atmosphere I def gonna come back. ", "In addition, maybe it\u2019s just me but i really wish the music was a bit more loud, it was so quite that i could hear people\u2019s conversation even we were 1 table away. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r600840661", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Deserved reputation", "diner_date": " July 2018", "rating_date": "29 July 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Vidmante M,", "Thank you for taking the time to write to us about your recent dining experience in our restaurant. Both our front of house and kitchen brigade are grateful for the kind words. We look forward to welcoming you back in the very near future.", "Kind regards,", "Domenico Pizzo", "Restaurant Manager at Peninsula restaurant "], "reviewer_pseudo": "Vidmante M", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r600840661-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["An excellent restaurant experience from beginning to end.", "I went for vegetarian tasting menu. Each dish was presented beautifully with strong flavours and textures. Skill, intelligence and imagination was apparent on each plate. Was hard to choose a favorite. Big thanks to chef Tomas and his team. ", "The service was impeccable, Olga and Domenico made sure of it. ", "I've been to plenty of Michelin starred restaurants and this ranks as one of the best, though has yet to achieve one."]}
