{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r586865190", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "A fantastic night out", "diner_date": " June 2018", "rating_date": "12 June 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Emiliano R,", "Thank you very much for your review. We are thrilled to see you enjoyed the views and had a good experience dining at Peninsula Restaurant. ", "We will be delighted to pass on your lovely feedback about our Chef and Colleagues who will be equally as pleased to hear such a fantastic review as they go above and beyond everyday to ensure all our guests experience only the best service. ", "Thank you once again for the lovely feedback and we are looking forward to welcoming you again", "Warm regards,", "Peninsula Restaurant Team"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Emiliano R", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r586865190-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Yes, the night scenario is quite evocative. And yes, you are in London and a bit thrilled for that. But apart from all this, the gist is that you're having a very special dinner cooked by a visionary chef that will soon be on everyone's lips (mark my words). The place is elegant but quite welcoming, even though it's the magnificent combo \"food + service\" that really deserves your attention and appreciation. Ask the staff for a piece of advice and they'll be glad to help out in no time. Then, let the food speak for itself and enjoy your dinner..."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r584564420", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Out of this world!", "diner_date": " May 2018", "rating_date": "2 June 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear ForeverLooking,", "Thank you for taking the time to write to us about your recent dining experience in our restaurant. Both our front of house and kitchen brigade are grateful for the kind words. We look forward to welcoming you back in the very near future.", "Kind regards,", "Domenico Pizzo", "Restaurant Manager at Peninsula restaurant "], "reviewer_pseudo": "ForeverLooking", "reviewer_origin": ["Lamphey, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "42"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "28"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r584564420-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["During our stay at the Intercontinental, we decided to pay a visit to the Peninsula restaurant. What we can stress enough is that if you go, you won't be disappointed! The variety is fantastic and caters for all. I, myself am a pescatarian and I was spoilt for choice. ", "When our meals came to the table, not only were they beautifully presented but the skill involved was obvious. Each mouthful was a delight and it was such a shame the meal had to come to an end. ", "We ordered from the normal menu, although upon reflection, we should have gone for the tasting menu. It is the one thing we regret. ", "The service is incredible. The staff are warm, friendly and go out of their way to make your time there an experience. ", "We would like to say a special thank you to Marco, Luis, and all the chefs that were involved with our meal. You do an amazing job and it is greatly appreciated!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r582125149", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellent restaurant", "diner_date": " May 2018", "rating_date": "23 May 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Clairehuff,", "Thank you very much for your review. We are thrilled to see you enjoyed the views and had a good experience dining at Peninsula Restaurant. ", "We will be delighted to pass on your lovely feedback about our Chef and Colleagues who will be equally as pleased to hear such a fantastic review as they go above and beyond everyday to ensure all our guests experience only the best service. ", "Thank you once again for the lovely feedback and we are looking forward to welcoming you again", "Warm regards,", "Peninsula Restaurant Team"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Clairehuff", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "8"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r582125149-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We ate here for our anniversary and enjoyed a wonderful tasting menu. I am a fussy eater (no meat, gluten free) and the chef was extremely accommodating by substituting our various dishes. ", "The food was great and the service in the restaurant was excellent. ", "Lovely views across Canary Wharf(ask for a window table). ", "Highly recommend having a drink before or after in the sky bar for even better views!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r584038345", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Elegance ", "diner_date": " May 2018", "rating_date": "31 May 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear tsunaminight,", "Thank you for taking the time to write to us about your recent dining experience in our restaurant. Both our front of house and kitchen brigade are grateful for the kind words. We look forward to welcoming you back in the very near future.", "Kind regards,", "Domenico Pizzo", "Restaurant Manager at Peninsula restaurant "], "reviewer_pseudo": "tsunaminight", "reviewer_origin": ["new york"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "97"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "35"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r584038345-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Very elegant and professional restaurant. All of the waitstaff were nice and it was great that the maitre\u2019d was so kind to seat us at a window table. We totally enjoyed the clean and quiet atmosphere. The food was amazing especially the duck and foie gras. The taste and texture were superb. It is definitely worth paying a visit for fine dining. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r582798905", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "So Much Better", "diner_date": " April 2018", "rating_date": "26 May 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear joe73634,", "Thank you for choosing to dine with us at Peninsula Restaurant; It is an absolute pleasure to read your review. We are so pleased that you found our restaurant welcoming and that you enjoyed both the food and service. Our staff genuinely cares very deeply about each and every guest and strive to provide the best customer experience to all. ", "Thank you once again for the great comments and we really hope you will decide to visit us again in the near future.", "Warm regards,", "Peninsula Restaurant Team"], "reviewer_pseudo": "joe73634", "reviewer_origin": ["Milton Keynes, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "50"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "56"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r582798905-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Had the tasting menu with the recommended wines and what a treat. The food was exquisite and the wines just complimented the taste of the food, now this is what a tasting menu should be based on. Kudos to the restaurant and chefs you've done a fabulous job, will be back."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r584690394", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fantastic! Just go!", "diner_date": " June 2018", "rating_date": "3 June 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear lindsayjparry, ", "We are delighted that you chose to celebrate your birthday celebration with us at the restaurant and thank you for your positive feedback. ", "As We sincerely value our guest\u2019s feedback and, entire team joins me in sending our heartfelt thanks. ", "I look forward to welcoming you back to enjoy future menus which evolve throughout the seasons.", "With kindest regards,", "Domenico Pizzo", "Restaurant Manager at Peninsula restaurant"], "reviewer_pseudo": "lindsayjparry", "reviewer_origin": ["Greater London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "5"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r584690394-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["My husband took me there for a surprise birthday dinner. We had the most fantastic meal with an amazing view across the Thames to Canary Wharf. Marco and the rest of the staff were superb and gave a relaxed and attentive service. Just perfect. The Sky bar on the eighteenth floor is also worth a visit and Sara there also looked after us with great cocktails and another amazing view/table. We\u2019ve had meals in a number of well known Michelin starred restaurants.... and this one deserves to be amongst them as it\u2019s one of the best. Thank you Marco and team."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r583065791", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Surprisingly Excellent", "diner_date": " May 2018", "rating_date": "27 May 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear MarshallManson,", "Thank you very much for your review. We are thrilled to see you enjoyed the views and had a good experience dining at Peninsula Restaurant. ", "We will be delighted to pass on your lovely feedback about our Chef and Colleagues who will be equally as pleased to hear such a fantastic review as they go above and beyond everyday to ensure all our guests experience only the best service. ", "Thank you once again for the lovely feedback and we are looking forward to welcoming you again", "Warm regards,", "Peninsula Restaurant Team"], "reviewer_pseudo": "MarshallManson", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "103"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "67"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r583065791-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Okay. I'll admit: When I heard there was supposedly a top class restaurant at the O2, I actually laughed out loud. But investigations suggested it might not be so strange after all, and we decided to give it a try. We didn't regret it.", "We went to the Peninsula on a night when there was nothing on at the O2. That seems advisable, as we hear it can be pretty nuts on show nights.", "One other tip: Go a little early, and have a glass of champagne in the hotel's rooftop bar. The view from the restaurant (which is on the second floor) is excellent, but from the bar, it's out of this world.", "Our whole experience at the Peninsula was excellent. We went for the a la carte menu, which was fine, although I would happily return for the tasting menu. Service was super-attentive and high quality. And the food was delicious. ", "I suspect the Peninsula would harbour Michelin aspirations if it weren't for its location. As it is, it's well worth a visit. But go for a sunny day if you can. The view improves everything just that bit more."]}
