{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r562002411", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Disappointingly average", "diner_date": " January 2018", "rating_date": "21 February 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Sus86london,", "Thank you very much for choosing our restaurant for your dinner and for sharing your feedback with the TripAdvisor community.", "it is very regrettable that your experience was not as you were expected. We are certainly looking into each and every point that you have raised. we can assure you that it is not the kind of experience we wish our guest to encounter when having there dinner with us. ", "Please rest assured that this valuable feedback as been shared with all the Peninsula teams and we will use it to enhance our training programs. ", "On a second note, I am please to learn that our team were very welcoming and made you feel like a regular.", "We really look forward to welcoming you back to the Peninsula restaurant and hope we show you the improvement that we have made following on your feedback.", "Warm regards,", "Peninsula Restaurant Team"], "reviewer_pseudo": "sus86london", "reviewer_origin": ["Hertfordshire, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "167"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "124"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r562002411-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Given the reviews of this place, we booked dinner here expecting wonderful things but unfortunately we were left totally underwhelmed. As with the hotel, the restaurant is really nicely decorated and immaculately clean. The staff were also very welcoming, making us feel like regular guests from the moment we arrived. I was a little disappointed with the menu but that is a matter of taste and preferences, so we decided to go with the tasting menu to try a little of various dishes. Although it wasn't listed on any of the menus we also asked about a matching wine flight which they said they did offer. We ordered a couple of cocktails which although we were warned that they were coming from the bar downstairs, did take ages to arrive. We were then presented with some amuse-bouche to wet our appetite and they were quite nice - 3 different types, 2 of which were really tasty but the 3rd (a Kimchi samosa) was unbelievably bland - could have been anything inside but definitely wasn't Kimchi. We had finished these by the time our cocktails had arrived, and then another waiter brought us another set of amuse-bouche. The 1st course then arrived but was a good few minutes before anyone brought us our glasses of matching wines. The service seemed a bit disfunctional & sporadic, which wasn't due to lack of staff as there were plenty of people milling around, just didn't seem that teams were communicating with each other correctly. The food of each course was slightly disappointing, some more so than others - presentation was beautiful but lacked basic seasoning & flavours. Had the beauty of a delicious dish but the taste didn't back this up. Since we had chosen the matching wines, we also expected some description from a sommelier or equivalent but at one point the waiter seemed to just be reading the back of the bottle - we could have described the wine better than he did. Unfortunately the night didn't back up the high reviews & left us wondering what the hype is all about. Certainly won't be rushing back & wouldn't recommend it to fine food lovers - for the price, there is far better in London."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r562287208", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing experience !", "diner_date": " February 2018", "rating_date": "23 February 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear JessicaPrimera,", "Thank you very much for choosing our restaurant for your celebration and sharing your experience with us.", " We are so happy to hear that you had a pleasant evening. As you mentioned in your review, we are really passionate about what we do and always trying to improve in order to make every single guest to feel very special. ", "From all Peninsula Restaurant Team, we would like to thank you again and we look forward to welcome you back very soon!", "Warm regards,", "Peninsula Restaurant Team"], "reviewer_pseudo": "jessicaprimera", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "12"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "15"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r562287208-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["My husband and I celebrate our anniversary there and the experience was pretty pleasant. Nice food and good service. We had the tasting menu and it was incredible. at the end of our meal they gave a beautiful complementary dessert for our anniversary. Amazing view of the Thames and Canary wharf"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r562382174", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Not just a meal, an amazing experience!", "diner_date": " February 2018", "rating_date": "23 February 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Busylizzi18,", "Thank you very much for the kind word, it is true that the Eighteen sky bar have amazing view on Canary wharf and is the perfect place to have your pre-dinner drink.", " We are pleased that you found our restaurant welcoming and that you enjoyed food and service. Our staff genuinely care and strive to provide the best customer experience to all our guests.", "Thank you once again for the great comments and we really hope you will decide to visit us again!", "Warm regards,", "Peninsula Restaurant Team"], "reviewer_pseudo": "busylizzie18", "reviewer_origin": ["Hastings, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "15"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r562382174-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I had been given a voucher for a meal as a gift and no prior knowledge of the hotel or restaurant. First of all we went up to the 18th floor bar, with stunning views over the river, for cocktails. We then went for our meal in the restaurant with the same lovely view. The staff were all friendly, knowledgeable and attentive. Our meals were beautifully presented, flavoured and absolutely delicious, with little extra treats before and afterwards. It was a fantastic experience - and one I highly recommend and intend to repeat! Thank you to all concerned"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r562383668", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "The least remaining truly incredible restaurant in London?", "diner_date": " February 2018", "rating_date": "23 February 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Davidnashfood,", "Thank you very much for choosing to have your dinner with us and sharing your experience, we are very please to see that you enjoy your experience.", "We will pass you comment to all teams in Peninsula restaurant. Our staff genuinely care and strive to provide the best customer experience to all our guests. ", "Thank you once again for the great comments and we hope to welcome you again in a near future.,", "Warm regards, Peninsula Restaurant Team"], "reviewer_pseudo": "davidnashfood", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "11"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "8"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r562383668-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Once upon a time there were a few restaurants in London with truly incredible food, service and wine list. ", "Then Hawksmoor started serving steak nearly cold and pre-bought desert wine 10 minutes after desert itself. Amd then Goucho reduced it's previously stellar service standards 1000%.", "Not that the Peninsula is a steak house. But this might be the last place in London to offer truly incredible service, food and an incredible wine list.", "The '7 course' (really 9 course) tasting menu is incredible, though a little tricky to finish. The fine wine pairing is even more incredible, and at \u00a380 represents exceptional value for money given it includes a \u00a350 glass of wine and virtually as many fine wines as courses.", "Best is the service. Attentive, speedy and with great knowledge of the wine. Seemingly impossible to find in London now, at least when coupled with such an extensive wine list. ", "And this entire assessment excludes the fact there is an actual view of the outside world; a pretty decent one looking out over the river and Canary Wharf through floor to ceiling glass walls, a view which almost no central London restaurants can offer, no matter how decorated their walls."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r562735385", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Just gets better and better", "diner_date": " February 2018", "rating_date": "25 February 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear ChrisLogan63,", "Thank you very much for choosing to have your dinner with us and for sharing your experience.", "We are very please to see that you had a relaxing evening with us, our February offer was a steal at \u00a329, but our early dinner menu is a very good value as well at \u00a335 for three courses.", "Our staff, chefs and waiters genuinely care and strive to provide the best customer experience to all our guests, and we are very please to see that they deliver a very good standard.", "As you mention the view from the restaurant are breath taken and i have to say with the spring approaching the sunset over Canary Wharf is amazing.", "Once again thank you very much for the kind words and we are looking forward to welcoming you again in a near future.", "Warm regards, ", "Peninsula Restaurant Team"], "reviewer_pseudo": "christine l", "reviewer_origin": ["Kent, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "310"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "123"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r562735385-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Just love this restaurant it has a lovely laid back give that makes you totally unwind and relax. Amazing staff who are friendly and attentive without being overbearing and then there is the Chef with his wonderful creations. We had the pre show meal \u00a329 per person for 3 courses including a chapeldown sparkling wine. It was incredible amuse bouche homemade bread starter main dessert and petit fours it was faultless the shortrib beef was well worth the \u00a35 supplement. Can't wait to return. Oh and did I mention the views!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r565161028", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Better than the Ledbury... impeccable", "diner_date": " September 2017", "rating_date": "7 March 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Dana F,", "Thank you very much for your review. We are thrilled to see you enjoyed the views and had a good experience dining at Peninsula Restaurant. ", "We will be delighted to pass on your lovely feedback about our Chef and Colleagues who will be equally as pleased to hear such a fantastic review as they go above and beyond everyday to ensure all our guests experience only the best service. ", "Thank you once again for the lovely feedback and we are looking forward to welcoming you again", "Warm regards,", "Peninsula Restaurant Team"], "reviewer_pseudo": "772danaf", "reviewer_origin": ["Greater London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "23"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "14"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r565161028-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["It's a bit strange writing a review of a restaurant I visited some months ago, but we have been doing a tour of new restaurants lately and we keep talking about how nothing is as good as the Peninsula was. Even the Ledbury was a letdown.", "I can't give you specifics of what I ate, but it was all excellent. The service was impeccable. As I said, we are still talking about what a lovely experience it was months later.", "My only complaint is something that they can't help - the walk to the hotel from the station is not very pedestrian friendly and feels like the middle of nowhere. I have to wonder if the location is the reason the restaurant was so quiet when we visited. I remember commenting that I couldn't believe they weren't fully booked, as the quality was so high."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r564569373", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Exceptional food and service", "diner_date": " March 2018", "rating_date": "5 March 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Anna M, ", "Thank you for your review regarding your visit to Peninsula Restaurant.", "We really appreciate you taking the time to share your experience with us. We count ourselves lucky for customers like you and we look forward welcoming you again in the future.", "Best regards,", "Domenico Pizzo", "Restaurant Manager at Peninsula restaurant"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Anna M", "reviewer_origin": ["Oxfordshire, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r564569373-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Exceptional food and service, fantastic quality and lovely touches at the beginning and the end. I had the goats cheese and beetroot starter which was divine, my partner had the fois gras, both of them so tasty, wonderful presentation! We both had the black cod for main with a side of chips and salad to share, the chips were fantastic, the salad was disappointing unfortunately, just a bowl of leaves - not what we were expecting for the price. Fantastic cheese trolley which we thought was really good value, a great choice of cheese which were all amazing, a real treat! Wine was lovely, however, it could have done with being more chilled, the ice bucket helped, but it took to near the end of the bottle before reaching the required temperature. However, overall I would highly recommend this restaurant, fantastic unobtrusive service, lovely ambiance and amazing food - we went before heading to the 02 for a concert, perfect timing of 2 hours, would recommend for a special occasion also, will try the taster menu next time!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r550126708", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "A Delightful Celebration ", "diner_date": " December 2017", "rating_date": "30 December 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "C6646DNjaneh", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "48"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "17"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r550126708-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We enjoyed a truly wonderful evening here. The staff were friendly, helpful and rightly proud of their excellent menu. As non meat eaters, it was really welcome to find three great fish options as well as three for vegetarians. The food was really excellent: beautifully presented and the flavours were wonderful. Our son thought it was the best meal he had had in a restaurant. And the setting is terrific- London\u2019s Manhattan. A real treat. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r552865332", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Wonderful food, views,service and value", "diner_date": " January 2018", "rating_date": "10 January 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "ClareUK123", "reviewer_origin": ["Auckland Central, New Zealand"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "106"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "34"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r552865332-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["What a great restaurant! I visited this restaursnt with my parents between Christmas and New year and would recommend it to everyone! We had the pre theatre menu which is around 35 pounds for 3 courses,probably the best value fine dining I have experienced!", "The food is beautifully presented and delicious with experimental flavours such as a smoked chocolate cake.", "The palette cleansers between courses were a delight.", "The service was spot on, the right balance of being of explaining the dishes and always available to help without being overbearing.", "The city views are also stunning. If you are considering eating here,do it! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r560875684", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Outstanding experience", "diner_date": " February 2018", "rating_date": "16 February 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear \"Aurelija N\",", "Thank you for choosing to dine with us! It is a pleasure to read your review about Peninsula Restaurant. We are pleased that you found our restaurant welcoming and that you enjoyed food and service. Our staff genuinely care and strive to provide the best customer experience to all our guests.", "Thank you once again for the great comments and we really hope you will decide to visit us again!", "Warm regards,", "Peninsula Restaurant Team"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Aurelija N", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r560875684-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Great restaurant, amazining food and very attentive staff. Did enjoy every moment being there! Thanks to EKaterina who made our evening even more special! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r553379628", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Incredible Experience ", "diner_date": " April 2017", "rating_date": "12 January 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "lcamacho", "reviewer_origin": ["Bainbridge Island, Washington"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "82"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "39"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r553379628-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["This is not exactly a restaurant a tourist to London would accidentally find as it is located at the top of a hotel in the business district, but we are so glad a local made the recommendation. We found it much more intimate than the Shard and the food was impressive. Would you normally take your kids to this restaurant? No. But, we were on vacation and didn\u2019t have access to babysitters so they went with us. Our kids are also adventurous diners and have very good manners so it wasn\u2019t an issue. The staff was so sweet and accommodating. The views from the restaurant are incredible. Business dinners and romantic dates composed most of the diners. ", "We did the 7-course chef tasting menu because everything sounded so creative and delicious. The food was impeccable and the wine pairing was perfect. Instead of assuming you will like their choices, they discovered my husband like big, bold reds and made a switch during one course that made my husband so happy. We spent an inordinate amount of time at dinner (3 hours!) and enjoyed every second of the experience. We highly recommend the Peninsula Restaurant and can\u2019t wait to go back when we return to London!"]}
