{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r554668794", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellent service, great view and superb food", "diner_date": " January 2018", "rating_date": "18 January 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Adrian H,", "Thank you for choosing to have a dinner in Peninsula Restaurant. We are very happy to hear that you had a wonderful time. ", "Ionut is indeed is a valuable member of our team and he is delighted to know that he has positively impacted on your stay. ", "We are looking forward to welcoming you back to us again in the nearest future!", "Warm regards,", "Peninsula Restaurant Team"], "reviewer_pseudo": "adrianharcau", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r554668794-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We were really impressed by the spectacular view and the attention to detail that we received from the chef and the staff in particular \"Ionut\". Thank you for a great evening and we felt valued from the moment we stepped into the restaurant. Highly recommended!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r559725020", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Wonderful Evening", "diner_date": " February 2018", "rating_date": "11 February 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear \"F C\",", "Thank you very much for celebrating your wedding anniversary with us! We are so happy to hear that you had a wonderful evening. As you mentioned in your review, we are really passionate about what we do and always trying to improve in order to make every single guest to feel very special. ", "From all Peninsula Restaurant Team, we would like to thank you again and we look forward to welcome you back very soon!", "Warm regards,", "Peninsula Restaurant Team"], "reviewer_pseudo": "733fc", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r559725020-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We chose to dine at the Peninsula Restaurant while we were staying at the Intercontinental Hotel for our wedding anniversary. ", "My husband and I both opted for the tasting menu. What an absolute delight from start to finish. The food was interesting, delicious, well balanced and the courses were perfectly spaced.", "The staff were extremely welcoming and everyone we came into contact with was polite, attentive, knowledgeable and genuinely seemed to love what they were doing. ", "To the team at the Peninsula Restaurant thank you for such a lovely evening we will definately return!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r560283282", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellent", "diner_date": " February 2018", "rating_date": "13 February 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear \"Nataliaailatan2017\",", "Thank you for choosing to dine and celebrate your Birthday in Peninsula Restaurant. We are delighted to hear that you had a great evening and you enjoyed the food. ", "Please accept our most sincere apologies with regards to the slow service on that night. This is definitely not a reflection of our usual service standards. ", "Our team is looking forward to welcome you back in the near future.", "Warm regards,", "Peninsula Restaurant Team"], "reviewer_pseudo": "nataliaailatan2017", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "35"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "22"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r560283282-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Excellent food, as always. Friendly service, but a little on the slow side this evening. A really lovely birthday meal with the family."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r560843673", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellent Dinner ", "diner_date": " February 2018", "rating_date": "16 February 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear \"Jana D\",", "Thank you very much for your review. We are very happy to see you enjoyed the views and had a good experience within Peninsula Restaurant. ", "We will be happy to pass on your lovely feedback about our Chef and Colleagues who will be equally pleased to hear such a fantastic review about them as they go above and beyond to ensure all our guests experience only the best service with us. ", "\"Jana D\" thank you once again for the lovely feedback and we are looking forward to welcoming you again!", "Warm regards,", "Peninsula Restaurant Team"], "reviewer_pseudo": "51janad", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "18"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "9"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r560843673-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Amazing Restaurant with excellent service, food and incredible views. The food was absolutely wonderful, from preparation to presentation, very pleasing. Special thank you for chef and Jekaterina who made our evening unforgettable. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r544613109", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Very good fine dining", "diner_date": " November 2017", "rating_date": "2 December 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "JuanCUK85", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "110"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "18"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r544613109-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["The service was excellent and the views from the restaurant were amazing. The tasting menu was original and had some good and original courses. The meat was absolutely delicious. It is great for special occasions and the service did everything in their hands to make us feel like aristocracy. The only drawback is perhaps the price, as it costs as much as manyMichelin starred restaurants...without the stars. "]}
