{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r544656811", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fantastic ", "diner_date": " December 2017", "rating_date": "2 December 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Tamandsharkie", "reviewer_origin": ["Oxford, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "6"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r544656811-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Went with my partner and his mother. I had lobster and crab ravioli, lamb and the cheese platter. All great. Apparently the cod main was lovely too and the partridge and pork starters. They do a tasting menu too, which we will come back and try. ", "Absolutely fantastic food and great service. Really good views too. Would highly recommend. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r547342310", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Perfect for a romantic night", "diner_date": " December 2017", "rating_date": "15 December 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Greg W", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r547342310-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["The food here was absolutely amazing. Portion sizes are perfect. The view is gorgeous and the tables are positioned in a way to make your dining experience feel really private and personal. Staff are friendly, knowledgeable, attentive but not intrusive. Gave my partner a free dessert after we had paid when they heard it was her birthday. Couldn't fault any part of our evening."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r547893453", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Could be great but a bit disappointed", "diner_date": " December 2017", "rating_date": "18 December 2017", "answer_text": ["Dear NotEasyPlease10,", "Thank you very much for choosing Peninsula restaurant for your pre show dinner, it was a pleasure to welcome you and your guest.", "Our team of chefs, always try to be innovative regarding there menu and we are sorry to hear that you did not like our smoked chocolate cake.", "We hope to see you again soon.", "The Peninsula team"], "reviewer_pseudo": "NotEasilyPleased10", "reviewer_origin": ["Christchurch, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "88"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "37"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r547893453-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Fantastic views (we were give a great corner table so had great views of the Thames in both directions) and very handy for the O2. Friendly and efficient staff - not over bearing or \u201csniffy\u201d at all. We chose from the pre show menu as we were going to a concert. The choices available all sounded lovely and each one we had had elements that were great but one or two bits let down the dish from being wow and fantastic, e.g smoked chocolate cake - the smokiness giving it an odd savoury taste that actually made it unpleasant and I couldn\u2019t finish it. Without the smoke it would have been sublime. Complimentary puffed rice and dips, fresh homemade rosemary bread and then a mushroom tart amuse bushe set the scene. Everything is superbly presented. Wines by the glass a little expensive although the pre show menu is a steal for this quality. Would come again but would maybe choose more wisely the dishes to have."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r543939739", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Early dinner", "diner_date": " November 2017", "rating_date": "29 November 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "janpeace55", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r543939739-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["The setting is spectacular but sadly we were treated poorly . The food was nice but over priced for what one received. One waiter was very patronising and never smiled once . He seemed irritated that we didn't want expensive wine so made us feel uncomfortable. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r540059531", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing food with amazing view", "diner_date": " October 2017", "rating_date": "10 November 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "BiancaS1307", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r540059531-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We went on a weekend trip to London at the end of October and decided to treat ourselves to a fine dining experience for my birthday. We did a bit of research and chose to book a table at the Peninsula restaurant in Greenwhich as we had heard and read good things about it (check out the headchef\u00b4s creative dishes on Instagram :)) . ", "The restaurant did not disappoint - we went for the tasting menue, my boyfriend had the \"standard\" version, I had the vegetarian option - both menues were very varied, creative, with amazing flavours and great plating. During the entire dinner the staff were friendly and attentive. ", "Also - the view is absolutely amazing, especially at night, so make sure to take some photos. :)", "The Peninsula restaurant is definitely worth a visit, we really enjoyed our time there-", "Thanks for a great birthday dinner!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r543120854", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing place ", "diner_date": " November 2017", "rating_date": "25 November 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Kristina D", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "21"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "9"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r543120854-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We have been to this restaurant a few times and this time we celebrated friends birthday. Had main tasting menu with matching wines. They had changed menu for Christmas and it was exquisite! Love all the flavours this talented chef brings together. I would highly recommend this place! Can\u2019t wait to go back !"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r541223568", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellent meal", "diner_date": " August 2017", "rating_date": "15 November 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Malcolm J", "reviewer_origin": ["Beckenham, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "17"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "12"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r541223568-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["The approach to the hotel by foot is a little downbeat but the hotel interior is very grand.", "Restaurant is large but when seated we felt in an intimate space.", "We were seated by the huge windows with a great view over the Thames.", "Service impeccable.", "Food and wine delicious.", "Will definitely return when we have an opportunity."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r542020619", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "superb evening", "diner_date": " November 2017", "rating_date": "19 November 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "gordon_aitken", "reviewer_origin": ["Cardiff, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "36"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "19"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r542020619-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We were attending a conference at Excel and were looking for somewhere nice nearby to dine. Going on the trip advisor reviews we opted for the Peninsula Restaurant at the Intercontinental Hotel by the 02. Only a \u00a314 Uber from our hotel. The restaurant was superb. Throughout the team were friendly and efficient. The Views over Canary Wharf are stunning . Food wise we went for the tasting menu with matching wines. Every course was unique , delicious and all the elements complimented each other. The paired wines were also very good. Not cheap but very good value for money. We will definitely be eating here again."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r543462706", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Perfect Dinner", "diner_date": " November 2017", "rating_date": "26 November 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Eivydas R", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r543462706-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["A superb fine dining experience with incredible Canary Wharf views and very cosy atmosphere. I decided to spend an evening with my girlfriend at Peninsula Restaurant and opted for tasting menu with wine pairing. The whole experience was amazing, and we were thrilled to taste each dish which was served. The service was seamless and waiters have put their best effort to make our dinner experience wonderful.", "Overall, there's no need to elaborate much on this review. Experience was truly wonderful, and even though the place is quite expensive, yet experience is 100% worth the price."]}
