{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r534338265", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "should be a michelin starred establishment", "diner_date": " August 2017", "rating_date": "19 October 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "stitchWirral_England", "reviewer_origin": ["wirral, england"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "33"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "49"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r534338265-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We had one of the best meals ever with the tasting men which catered for me as a vegetarian.", "Food was beautifully presented, with great flavour using trusted combinations and served by friendly staff.", "I wont spoil it by describing what we had -just go there and find out for yourself!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r534493366", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "My wife's birthday", "diner_date": " October 2017", "rating_date": "20 October 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "988alane", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r534493366-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We went to hotel for my wife's birthday for the weekend. My wife and children went to the peninsular restaurant on Friday for dinner. The waitress seemed very in experienced, I asked for the set menu she said it stopped at 7pm. I had check the web site and it said 7.30. When I pointed this out she went and checked the web site and I was right. So we were given the menu, but we were made to feel she was doing us a favour. When my wife said she wanted to order from the main menu. The waitress said we all had to order off the set menu, when I queried this, she went to see the manager and there was a very heavy discussion. Then she came back and said it was fine for us to mix. The set menu was fine for our children. The whole thing made me feel very uncomfortable, what was supposed to be a relaxed evening. The next night we had 13 for dinner in the market brassiere (the cheaper restaurant) the staff were perfect. The waitress was in tune with everything, she knew went ask about extra wine and the whole team came out and sang happy birthday to my wife. 5 stars Market Brasserie, try harder Peninsular."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r535325656", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Sublime Food and Views", "diner_date": " October 2017", "rating_date": "23 October 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Emma G", "reviewer_origin": ["Greater London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "33"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "11"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r535325656-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We chanced upon this restaurant when making a last-minute booking for date night and what a find! A short walk from the o2, the minute you step through its doors you are whisked away from the noises and flashing lights of the local area. We were seated at a window table, able to look at the lights of Canary Wharfs and the ships passing by on the river.", "We decided to try the tasting menu, at \u00a370 for 7 courses we thought this was good value and we certainly weren't disappointed! Each course comes out the perfect size, with no long waits between each one, each has its own flavouring and yet they all work together to form a meal. I was particularly impressed by the fish courses and absolutely blown away by the dessert. My boyfriend paired his meals with the wine tasting option and it was lovely to have the meal and wine explained at the start of each course so you could understand the intricacy which went into planning and pairing both. ", "The restaurant was quite quiet for a Friday night, which I thought was a shame as more people should definitely visit and enjoy this restaurant but it did mean that we received perfect service along with the perfect meal.", "Highly recommend."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r535507528", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing time ", "diner_date": " September 2017", "rating_date": "23 October 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Bartosz G", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r535507528-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I took my girlfriend to celebrate her birthday and that was best option, Mr Ucha served for us. We took set menu and he match every single dish whit different wine. Food was excellent, knowledge about every single detail on our plate", " is unbelievable. Food 5/5 knowledge 5/5 views 5/5. Thank you for your hospitality for all peninsula team! Well done! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r536882514", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing food and beautiful views!!!", "diner_date": " October 2017", "rating_date": "29 October 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Maikeld8", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r536882514-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Very impressed. amazing menu. Would recommend to everyone. Can fell there is a lot of skilled involved in their preparation! and the service was also really good, Ionut was really kind and was paying attention for the details, It was a really good experience!!!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r536484299", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Surprise after surprise ", "diner_date": " October 2017", "rating_date": "27 October 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "johnny_lambo", "reviewer_origin": ["Toronto, Canada"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "26"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r536484299-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Service is good. Surprises before meal during meal and after meal. ", "Plating is important for me. I come there not just to taste but enjoy the visual and experience. That's why I pay more to see if I would be pleased. ", " The European cuisine itself with a touch of fusion. It means you will find the dish which might be mixes with curry gravy. ", "The only one thing I don't enjoy its the sweet treats at the end. Its being serving on top of a bowl of raw barley grain. I picked up the sweet treat together with uncooked barely. It was a slight mishap. ", "Overall, lots of flavor in one dish which I would rather to have more coordinated flavor in a dish instead. Nothing wrong with that. It is just my preference. I still give it a five stars because of the surprised, and I can see the chef cooking with his passion and love. Not going to tell the readers here what surprised we received because you have to find them out yourself. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r535666967", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Don\u2019t go until the lighting has been repaired", "diner_date": " October 2017", "rating_date": "24 October 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "PeterBibby", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "122"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "160"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r535666967-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["The entrance to the Peninsula on the second floor of the Intercontinental Hotel looks more like a night club than a grand restaurant (see picture).", "We came partly for the fabulous view of Canary Wharf, but it was ruined by a lighting disaster. The restaurant interior is lit like a prison camp so brightly that we could scarce see the view (see picture). We were helpfully moved to a somewhat better table. Staff explained that the lighting controls had failed. ", "The modern English menu is commendably short; seven starters and eight mains. I started with scallops served with mussel sauce and a variety of small mushroom. The scallops were served on a cloud generator (see picture). For the main course I had duck with quince and foie gras toast. The big, flat, heavy, plate was cold and as was the puddle of jus (see picture). A companion said that their cod was cold. The fois gras toast was served separately on a rock, so I missed it until later.", "The food and presentation is complicated and impressive. The service and style is old-fashioned formal with all our choices delivered simultaneously by a team of staff. The meal started with an amuse bouche of crackers with dips and finished with sweet nibbles. There is, unfortunately, canned music. The cost per person, excluding alcohol but including water, coffee and the service charge, was \u00a364."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r536986483", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great pre-show O2 meal", "diner_date": " October 2017", "rating_date": "29 October 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "SarahS6813", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "117"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "33"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r536986483-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Restaurant itself was a little further than O2 than other restaurants, but excellent service and meal. Excellent pre-show meal, highly recommend the gnocchi. Would visit again."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r534165717", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellent is the right word", "diner_date": " October 2017", "rating_date": "18 October 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Christophe D", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "8"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r534165717-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I really recommend the experience not only to enjoy the view of the impressive new city of Canary Wharf but the talent of chef Tomas Lidakevicius is just very high quality in every details.But I could not forget the service team who brings the extra touch to serve this lovely menu I want to mention Eva and Ionut who have been fantastic host"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r531952577", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Great View", "diner_date": " September 2017", "rating_date": "11 October 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "HXK105", "reviewer_origin": ["Greater London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r531952577-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We had a meal in the Private Dining area of the Peninsula Restaurant. The restaurant catered for us picky eaters with the choices available and the staff were great with the service and brought out the food in a timely manner.", "The food wasn't all that special, part of my main meal was so salty it left the inside of my feeling shriveled up! I didn't mention it at the time as I was with a large group celebrating a birthday and didn't want to put a dampener on the occasion. The rest of the food was fine. I would expect everything to be perfect at these prices."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r532759889", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Chef Tomas and his team are magnificent! ", "diner_date": " October 2017", "rating_date": "14 October 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Daniel d", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r532759889-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I can only congratulate the team for the 3 AA rosettes they been recently awarded and I hope they get the Michelin star that they well deserve.", "Dinner was simply amazing. The atmosphere was great. F&B service was remarkable, always attentive but not overwhelming and very polite. And the food was like music to my ears. Beautiful presentation, garnishes really tasty and that beef ribs....a MUST. ", "Highly recommended! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r530796073", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "More please!", "diner_date": " October 2017", "rating_date": "7 October 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "duck_detective", "reviewer_origin": ["Brussels, Belgium"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "32"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "15"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r530796073-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I went here with my family for a fancy diner whilst on city trip in London after reading all the lovely reviews, and we were not disappointed! ", "From the moment we stepped into the restaurant untill we left, service was very attentive. We decided to go with the tasting menu. However, we are all allergic to seafood. So, it was no problem at all to switch out the seafood dish for a vegetarian option. Every course looked splendid and tasted good. The views are magnificent! My mom is not a big drinker and just wanted a single glass of wine. The sommelier had her try a few different options, so she could decide what she liked best. She really appreciated the gesture.", "One minor point: the paired wines with the tasting menu could use a step-up in my opinon. ", "Would certainly recommend this restaurant!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r531579472", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great service !!!", "diner_date": " October 2017", "rating_date": "10 October 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "aramiez567", "reviewer_origin": ["Madrid, Spain"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r531579472-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["The atmosphere of the restaurant was fantastic. I love how clean the bathrooms were and how accommodating they were with my family and me. Thank you so much for a great experience."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r530540116", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "A great evening with good food and excellent service", "diner_date": " October 2017", "rating_date": "6 October 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Peter T", "reviewer_origin": ["Edinburgh, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "113"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "46"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r530540116-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["This restaurant came on a recommendation from a work colleague who I would listen to again. ", "The quality of the food is excellent, the service welcoming and genuine. At first within the group there was some comments on the high prices however once fed and watered it was worth every penny, and we would go back again. ", "apparently it can get busy at weekends so it might be wise to book early. Enjoy"]}
