{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r533636903", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Exceptional food with views to match", "diner_date": " October 2017", "rating_date": "17 October 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "UKFinnGirl", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "37"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "26"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r533636903-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Tucked next to the O2 Arena in London is the second Hotel Intercontinental in London and if you\u2019ve ever stayed there, you know their high standards (but more about the hotel in another review). Inside on the second floor this beautiful restaurant overlooking the river Thames. Quiet and deceptively unassuming, but don\u2019t let the first impressions fool you. The cooking is exceptional as is the service. We thoroughly enjoyed our dinner!", "As we were going to see a show we had no time for the tasting menu, which would be our first choice. But the a la carte didn\u2019t disappoint.", "On paper, the menu choices look seemingly simple. Titles read e.g. \u2018Partridge\u2019, \u2018\u2019Cod\u2019, \u2018Lamb\u2019 with some ingredients listed underneath. Again, what you are presented with show exceptional technique and understanding of flavour- nothing simple here!", "I had the partridge and it was delectable. For main I had the lamb and I must say, what a wonderful land it was. It came with a piece of fillet perfectly cooked. But the highlight of the dish was a lamb croquet and I don\u2019t like croquettes normally, but they changed my mind - I could have eaten a whole plateful! My husband had the crab and cod, both gorgeous too.", "And then there was dessert. Beetroot Field. Lovely, sweet, with marvellous textures. I\u2019d go back just for that! ", "All accompanied with great wines and exceptional service. ", "We\u2019ll be back for that tasting menu!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r533247614", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Very nice ", "diner_date": " October 2017", "rating_date": "15 October 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Alison M", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r533247614-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Excelent service and atmosphere. ", "Fresh food and really tasty!!!", "Very nice to have a dinner o lunch with your partner. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r528072373", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great - if you don't mind a two-hour roundtrip to Mayfair", "diner_date": " September 2017", "rating_date": "28 September 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Leara K", "reviewer_origin": ["New York City, New York"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "57"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "34"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r528072373-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Decided to dine there because of the great reviews and the scenic views. We took a taxi from the theatre on Shaftesbury Ave around 5:15pm and arrived at the Peninsula at 6:35. That's a loooong drive. The restaurant is in a new hotel (in the middle of seemingly nowhere) and beautiful. Lobby and restaurant staff very friendly. Although the restaurant was still almost empty when we arrived, our request for a table different than the one we were shown was denied. The food was creative, pretty to look at and delicious. We did not order from the prix fixe menu; as a result, the attention of our waitstaff was noticeably diminished. The bill was manageable. And then the drive back ... 55 minutes to our Marble Arch hotel. Not sure why no other reviewers have mentioned this two-hour waste of time and taxi fares, but seems worth sharing."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r530130992", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great service and food", "diner_date": " September 2017", "rating_date": "5 October 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "vegazbabz", "reviewer_origin": ["Copenhagen, Denmark"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "61"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "14"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r530130992-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We were greeted by a lady who immediately made a table with seaside view available for us. After we ordered, the kitchen served 3 small starter courses for us (we only order the main courses). That was a great service and addition.", "For main course we had the Surrey-farm Beef Short Rib with hand cut chips and Wild Rabbit with seasonal green vegetables.", "As for any high-end restaurant, the portion sizes are not massive, however, the quality is excellent and you will decently full afterwards. The Short Rib was super tender and the fries were crispy and had a good size. The rabbit was also great, with different pieces of rabbit. Seasonal side was alright, wasn't my taste but my partner liked it.", "We were not so hungry, so we did not order dessert. But they have a huge cheese-table.", "Service from staff was excellent - but with a 12.5% service fee included in the bill, I guess that is how it should be.", "The price is high-end even for Danes, who are used to pay when we go out.", "The view over the financial district during evening/night is very pretty and cozy.", "I will recommend this for anyone who would like a good evening with good food - just bring you wallet."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r528728657", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Pre o2 shiw", "diner_date": " October 2017", "rating_date": "1 October 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Journey588577", "reviewer_origin": ["Cowbeech, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r528728657-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["What a lovely restaurant ", "The waitress young girl was absolutely fantastic, knew her job really well and keen to advise us on the method used to cook the food a real asset to her employer", "The food was fantastic crab starters really fresh and the avocado sponge was a real treat", "I had the halibut and my wife had cod and both were fantastic ", "Parking to the restaurant was easy and a lot cheaper than parking in the o2 and a lot quicker leaving the o2 event after ", "Definitely recommend this restaurant and we had a river view which was a nice touch go there you will not be disappointed "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r529328139", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Evening dinner", "diner_date": " October 2017", "rating_date": "3 October 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "g1farrell", "reviewer_origin": ["Hollingbourne, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r529328139-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Excellent service and excellent food.", "Arrived early and had a drink in the bar overlooking the Thames and Canary Warf. Was seated for dinner again with a spectacular view. What a great way to start the evening before going to a show at the O2 which is conveniently connected to the hotel. A fab evening all round."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r529671605", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Brilliant!", "diner_date": " September 2017", "rating_date": "3 October 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Shenda F", "reviewer_origin": ["Greater London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r529671605-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["The food and service is amazing. The views fabulous. It\u2019s the second time we have been and every time they made us feel very special. Highly recommend "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r529427661", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great Restaurant but Location Challenged", "diner_date": " October 2017", "rating_date": "3 October 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Joe K", "reviewer_origin": ["Houston, Texas"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "224"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "113"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r529427661-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Rated as the third best in London on TripAdvisor, we thought it was worth the visit to the south east side of the Thames. The restaurant has fantastic views of the river and modern buildings on the north side. ", "The food was very good, we had Scallop (better) and the Cornish Crab appetizers, followed by the Halibut and Beef Fillet (my preferred entree) and Gran Marnier Mousse (not much Gran Marnier taste) and Ice Cream Sorbet.", "The service was good, but slacked at the end as the dining area filled. I had to remind them to add my wine to the bill, which they had forgotten about...I thought the bill was a little low!", "Overall, very nice evening but much better if you're staying in the area. We took a CROWDED tube to the restaurant from Mayfair, which was about 50 minutes at 17:30 rush hour, then a 45 pound taxi ride back. Apparently, there is not an easy way to get to this restaurant from the city / Mayfair."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r529921008", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Nice food at an affordable price", "diner_date": " July 2017", "rating_date": "4 October 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Casecas", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "55"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "21"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r529921008-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["You can find very nice dim sum up to 5pm, with a very acceptable price.", "The place is very convenient if you are driving (parking free for clients) and it is a very big restaurant.", "It is not glamorous, but very nice for a Sunday lunch with your family."]}
