{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r525782627", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "THE best restaurant I've ever been to", "diner_date": " September 2017", "rating_date": "19 September 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "tokidokidoki", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "27"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "31"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r525782627-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["My fianc\u00e9 took me to the Peninsula Restaurant as a birthday treat last week. From start to finish the entire experience was absolutely amazing. The staff were wonderful: really attentive, warm, and knowledgable. The food was even better! I had the wild rabbit main while he had the lamb. Both were cooked to absolute perfection. I would love to go back in future (although most likely not for some time - it's definitely not in our usual price range!) and would definitely recommend the Peninsula to anybody looking for a special venue for a romantic, intimate treat."]}
