{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r518972336", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing evening", "diner_date": " August 2017", "rating_date": "29 August 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Juste A", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r518972336-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["As you enter this restaurant you are welcomed by an excellent setting of it. We were sitting by the window with an amazing view. We had \"Tasting menu\" for our dinner and all the dishes were absolutely great with the best quality and fresh products. The service was very pleasant and attentive. I highly recommend this restaurant for everybody!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r520460277", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Very good but a bit too expensive ", "diner_date": " September 2017", "rating_date": "2 September 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "chadpunk", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "27"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "26"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r520460277-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["It was very good. Definitely a place for a special occasion. The food and service were all quite fancy but it wasn't so formal that you felt uncomfortable. Great setting looking over Canary Wharf. I'd say they maybe need to sort out the background music as it was all trumpets and plinky pianos so you felt like you were in a hotel. It's also just a teensy bit too pricey for what you get but overall it was worth the splash out. Definitely have the beef short rib. It was delicious. "]}
