{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r488992389", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great food, fantastic service", "diner_date": " May 2017", "rating_date": "30 May 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Jo G", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "95"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "57"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r488992389-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We ate at The Peninsula one evening and had such a great evening. The restaurant, although not huge, has a lovely atmosphere and of course has great views over Canary Wharf. The food was very very good and I would definitely recommend eating here. The staff are exceptional, particularly our waitress, Eva - fantastic service and added to our great evening. In fact, all the staff we encountered at the hotel were exceptionally helpful and polite. We ate here as part of a deal but we would definitely return."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r484113843", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "What an amazing dinner ", "diner_date": " May 2017", "rating_date": "14 May 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Ilona A", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r484113843-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Had a dinner last night with my husband at peninsula restaurant at the o2. We went for the 7 course tasting menu which was an amazing choice. From the start to the finish it was highest level. Staff probably best in London. Knowledge of all dishes and wines was top noch. And the food...flavours were well played and seasonal, perfectly seasoned. Presentation of food was highest level. Would recommend it to everyone to spend a romantic night with views, amazing food and service. Hope Michelin star is just round the corner!"]}
