{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r488382214", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing 7 course tasting menu! ", "diner_date": " April 2017", "rating_date": "28 May 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Vilmis Z", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "10"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "10"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r488382214-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We were celebrating my wife's birthday and reserved a table for 6. All of us had a superb evening, relaxing environment, delicious food and outstanding service. Head chef Tomas came to check on us and other guests even though the restaurant seemed fairly busy. It was one of the best tasting menus we had, accompanied with a good selection of wines. We have finished the night in the top floor sky bar with astonishing views, music and cocktails. 10 out of 10! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r488767109", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Birthday Celebrations ", "diner_date": " May 2017", "rating_date": "29 May 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "mark67710", "reviewer_origin": ["Hemel Hempstead, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "140"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "60"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r488767109-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Took my wife here as a special 50th birthday celebration and was very impressed. Beautiful surroundings and a lovely view of Canary Wharf and O2. Very attentive staff kept us feeling very homely and okay. Had a group-on deal for a 3 course meal including a glass of champagne. My was starter consisted of rolled beef brisket serve with a lovely jus and caviar and it was amazing, tasty and perfectly cooked. For mains had duck confit leg served with rhubarb and mini broccoli stems and potato. Once again stunning and packed full of flavour and perfectly cooked maybe slightly over cooked should have been a little more pink. Anyway lovely and moist and dessert was chocolate ice cream and torte and was lovely. We both had a very memorable and special meal and they even brought out a small birthday cake on a black slate with Happy Birthday written on it with white icing. Thank you guys for making this evening a memorable one and hope to be back again soon. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r488349832", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Faultless fine dinning experience :)", "diner_date": " April 2017", "rating_date": "28 May 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "PhoebeH360", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r488349832-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["It was one of our monthly friends gathering and we were carving for fine dinning experience. We ordered the 7 courses tasting menu and it was amazing :) The combination of food in every dishes shows the effort and hard work of the chefs :) it is just simply wonderful. The service is excellent that everyone is help with the knowledge of food and wine. Definitely coming back for the next tasting and really looking forward to it :)"]}
