{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r482016692", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellent night out", "diner_date": " May 2017", "rating_date": "6 May 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Rachael B", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "8"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r482016692-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["The staff were really attentive,but not overbearing .The service was impeccable and if the next course was a tiny bit late the staff came and advised us that the course was on it's way. The food was very well presented and very flavoursome.", "This resturant is part of the hotel intercontinental and steps away from the O2 centre. If I was on a city break I would use this hotel for the meal side of the event, followed by going to the O2 event and it would make a fantastic weekend."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r482251218", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Groupon deal", "diner_date": " May 2017", "rating_date": "7 May 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Alpenking123", "reviewer_origin": ["Greater London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "7"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r482251218-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We felt very special a real treat.", " Arriving by Thames Clipper from London Bridge then a 10 minute walk along the river to the hotel, made a lovely start to our evening. We were met by a friendly doorman who recommended drinks in the bar on the 18th floor, fabulous views over the river and O2. Recommend a visit to the loo for the view from floor to ceiling windows!", "Dinner in the Peninsula Restaurant was lovely. Starting with a glass of bubbly we had delicious cheffy food. Beautifully presented and unusual flavours. ", "Overall fantastic value deal. Would love to return and try the full menu and even stay over in the hotel."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r476587872", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Nice view, excellent food & service", "diner_date": " April 2017", "rating_date": "17 April 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Lafite64", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "20"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "8"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r476587872-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We went for a special birthday dinner, having both the vegetarian and regular tasting menus. The food was perfectly prepared and presented, the service impeccable."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r482973248", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing dinner at the Penninsula Restaurant Intercontinental Hotel", "diner_date": " May 2017", "rating_date": "9 May 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Paul N", "reviewer_origin": ["Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "8"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r482973248-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Having read previous reviews about this restaurant we had very high expectations and the whole experience certainly lived up to them iIt was ato a truly fantastic evening out Every member of staff was excellent and great attention was paid to detail and making The guest experience the best it could possibly be ", " We started with drinks at the bar on the 18th floor enjoying amazing views ,lovely early evening sunshine and excellent service ", "The food in the restaurant was truly outstanding .All dishes were beautifully and creatively displayed with exciting tastes and textures Nothing was too much trouble ", " We had finished the delicious canap\u00e9s and were offered more and also with the lovely home made bread and handmade batter ", " We cannot recommend this restaurant highly enough if you enjoy excellent ", "food service ambience luxury surroundings and wonderful views across London"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r472038746", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Stunning Place!", "diner_date": " April 2017", "rating_date": "2 April 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "chrisbE456VZ", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "5"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "9"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r472038746-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We went here expecting nothing like what we received, location is stunning and we even had free parking! The staff were amazing something you'd expect from a Michelin Star restaurant, has to be something they are trying for.. Views across the Thames towards the financial district were stunning, watching he sun set as you have dinner. Food was amazing! Again something not dissimilar from our visits to Michelin Star restaurants! I had the steak tartare to start, amazing!! My fianc\u00e9e had the salmon, tiny amount but unreal. We both had the plaice which again was beautiful, right amount of everything and the mix of flavours perfect! It was quiet but it's only been open for a year so a little gem, my advice is book now!! Start with a drink in the stunning eighteen bar and finish with a meal in this restaurant, I couldn't recommend more! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r471309005", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Delightful!", "diner_date": " March 2017", "rating_date": "30 March 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "beebeebee08", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "92"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "67"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r471309005-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["My boyfriend and I were at the Peninsula last evening to celebrate his birthday and we had a wonderful experience, from the beginning to the end. The dining room is spacious, classy and the views of Canary wharf and the river in the nightlights is very special.", "The food was beautifully presented, we had the 7 course menu and for most of the dishes, the flavours were well thought out and a tasty sensation, in particular the Cornish crab (very refreshing and delicate), the Anjou quail (cooked to perfection, succulent and well balanced with the peas), the cod fish had a most delightful seafood sauce accompaniment and the parfait was delicious.", "The floor staff were the highlight of this restaurant. They were professional, kind and is an example of what high level service should be at a fine dining restaurant. The floor staff provided wonderful details of each dish we were having and at the end of the meal, my boyfriend had a surprise birthday dessert plate with a candle and it really made our evening even more special. To the kind floor staff at the Peninsula, thank you for such a lovely experience.", "I would recommend this place for a celebratory or couple\u2019s night out, for out of towners visiting London or for anyone who would enjoy fine dining sophisticated food, in particular the degustation experience. We have been to a few Michelin star restaurants and this is comparable, in terms of quality of food and level of service. We will return!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r470319917", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Absolutely Divine!", "diner_date": " March 2017", "rating_date": "26 March 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "MWF00", "reviewer_origin": ["Maidenhead, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "49"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "75"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r470319917-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Amazing restaurant with gorgeous views of the city. The food is beautifully presented, looks delicious and tastes even better! With super fresh ingredients, exquisite flavours - each mouthful an absolute delight. Everything from the moment we entered the restaurant to the moment we left was perfect. Excellent front of house team delivering perfect service - spot on. I really cannot fault this place - the team have got this right and it won't be long before they are awarded their michelin stars!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r472035392", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "7 taster menu superb", "diner_date": " March 2017", "rating_date": "2 April 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "297ivyk", "reviewer_origin": ["Kenley, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r472035392-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I would highly recommend this restaurant and it's 5* service. Beautifully situated, lovely view from window seat, service was very friendly and lovely. Now what can I say about the food? Each course melted in my mouth, no exaggeration, literally the flavour was there complete with exceptional choices of wine to taste. The 7 course taster menu with the wine is a must! Just see the work of art below. Would come again."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r473893491", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great view, great views", "diner_date": " April 2017", "rating_date": "9 April 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "P0llym", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "22"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "16"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r473893491-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["What an amazing restaurant. Went with a friend for a birthday dinner and arrived early enough for a cocktail. We sat by the window looking out on the river watching the sun go down. Bar staff were warm and accommodating. Food was simply delicious and tasty, restaurant comfortable and it was nice to eat and talk without being drowned out by music. We had a very helpful waiter who steered us towards our choice of wine. The service was outstanding and staff smiled throughout. To finish, the chef sent us some small sweets nestled on a bed of sesame seeds. That was a lovely touch and we left feeling, 'this deserves another visit'. Try the Sky bar on the top floor. Terrific view with waiter/waitress service. We only wished our waitress served us with a smile! Overall, a classy place to dine out. And would definitely recommend it."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r472039577", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Stunning location and tasty food ", "diner_date": " April 2017", "rating_date": "2 April 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "JojoLJ_13", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "59"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "110"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r472039577-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["My fianc\u00e9 and I visited here last night and all I can say is amazing! From the moment you step into the restaurant the staff are so friendly and cannot do enough for you. So very attentive and pleasant. ", "The drinks menu is vast with wines cocktails and beers. I chose a glass of champagne and my fianc\u00e9 a draft lager. ", "To start I ordered the smoked salmon and my fianc\u00e9 the beef tartare, they were both presented beautifully and they tasted as good as they looked. ", "For main we both opted for the plaice which didn't let us down it was again beautifully presented and tasted great! It was delicious. ", "We didn't have desert but they bought over 3 miniature deserts each which was salted caramel truffle passion fruit cone and a white chocolate crunch ", "Overall we had such a lovely dining experience and we shall without doubt return. The whole place and atmosphere was great and the staff are just so lovely, and to top it off the view is stunning too! Keep doing what you are doing guys as you are definitely getting it right! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r473811648", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fantastic food and lovely setting", "diner_date": " April 2017", "rating_date": "9 April 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "NikhailB", "reviewer_origin": ["West Malling, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "166"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "73"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r473811648-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Went for the 7-course tasting menu with champagne. Lovely location - seated at a window table looking out onto canary wharf. The food was incredible. Each course was well presented and had great taste. They even managed to accommodate my wife's gluten intolerance. Service was friendly and prompt. Had a lovely meal and will return."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r475188082", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Super restaurant & staff", "diner_date": " April 2017", "rating_date": "13 April 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "David L", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r475188082-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["What can I say but excellent everything. The staff are all so friendly and Chef Tomas creates another spectacular tasting menu. Well done! My wife and I enjoy returning to the restaurant on a number of occasions. Need I say anymore...."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r475309802", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great value 3 course meal with class", "diner_date": " March 2017", "rating_date": "13 April 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Pokumon_London", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "59"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "22"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r475309802-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Booked a three course meal and a glass of Champagne for two people on Groupon for \u00a349.", "The restaurant had excellent views, with tasty food and attentive staff.", "I would recommend to anyone."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r469495359", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Posh, quiet, British", "diner_date": " March 2017", "rating_date": "22 March 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "fabsite", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "569"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "250"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r469495359-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Just 10 minutes walk from North Greenwich station / The O2, this is the only fine restaurant on this side of the Thames (at least within Greenwich borough).", "On the 2nd floor of the hotel, the setting is not only classy & beautiful but also perfect for business dinners. Service was also very attentive, thanks to the lovely & discreet Eva and Csaba. 5/5", "The set menu was well balanced with one vegetarian option per course.", "A few crackers with two dips, plus onion white or brown bread (with butter) to start the meal. Particularly, bread was freshly baked and perfect in salt! 4/5", "The chestnut gnocchi are a reinvention of standard gnocchi: they tasted like they were baked and, only after that, mixed with white sauce & parsnips, chicory is not really essential to be honest. I felt they could have been even better with more sauce/cream, flavours were decent but it remains a little dry to taste (chicory does not have any dressing). 3/5", "The bread & butter pudding was magnificent: light and full of flavours but white chocolate powder on cinnamon ice cream was the brilliant surprise. 5/5", "Downsides? Rather small portions and a little high prices.", "The Groupon deal - still available - at \u00a320 (\u00a325 including water and service) is a bargain, do give them a chance if you want to experiment fine British / Continental gems."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r460461258", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Valentines Dinner", "diner_date": " February 2017", "rating_date": "16 February 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "benj699", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "25"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "10"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r460461258-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Pleasant dining room, well spaced out with good views of the Wharf. Service was great and very friendly staff, extremely polite but room for improvement....certainly not a reason for not going. The food was good and I can see them gaining a great reputation long term. Certainly based on location and the fact it was a new hotel's restaurant it was as I expected it to be. They have a Sky Bar upstairs which we missed as were shattered but I'd imagine you could have a nice meal and some decent drinks upstairs so worth a visit."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r461074740", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great food and very friendly and professional service", "diner_date": " February 2017", "rating_date": "19 February 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Ryannl8", "reviewer_origin": ["Amsterdam, The Netherlands"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "91"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "45"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r461074740-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We were there on a Saturday night. The place was pretty full but not overcrowded. We were welcomed very friendly and got a table with a good view. Chairs and couch offered a very comfortable seating. The table was big and impeccable with white linen and stylish cutlery and glasses. The waiters were very friendly and made real contact which is always nice. The food was excellent. We chose the seven course tasting menu. The oister in champagne amuse was top, followed by salmon in beetroot. Very special combination with the sweet beetroot and the fish. This was followed by quail and hake and then also excellent beef. We concluded that we, as pretty spoiled europeans, have hardly ever eaten better and so refined in the UK, even though you cannot compare London with the UK. The wine was of fine quality too and not too expensive. The only negative thing we can think of is that it wasn't really a seven course menu, but actually five. But maybe thats a cultural thing. In our country you don't count an amuse and a spoom as a course but as a courtesy to your guests. But anyhow they tasted great. We can advise this place to everyone who wants a great meal in the higher ranks. And yes the view is impressing!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r462934522", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Elegant & refined ", "diner_date": " February 2017", "rating_date": "26 February 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Krishgau", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "49"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "24"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r462934522-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Being local Greenwich residents, this restaurant has been on our radar for quite a while. We visited the restaurant on Friday evening for dinner with friends. ", "The dining room is a beautiful space with great views of Canary Wharf. We opted for the 7 course tasting menu with the wine flight. The whole menu was exquisitely presented with tonnes of flavour. The cooking was easily of Michelin starred standard. The sommelier was very friendly and approachable. Overall, it was a fantastic evening and we will definitely be back again. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r464202057", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "OMG AMAZING", "diner_date": " March 2017", "rating_date": "3 March 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "janrennie", "reviewer_origin": ["Aylesbury, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "28"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "22"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r464202057-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["What can l say I'm lost for words which doesn't happen very often, my sister and l took our mum here for her 97th birthday on a Groupon voucher, We travelled form Camden by bus to the restaurant and were a bit tired as it was a fairly long journey but by God was it worth it. On entry to the hotel we were met by a very friendly concierge who escorted us up to the 2nd floor restaurant, we were shown to our table with wonderful views, the waiter even offfered mum a cushion for her back, the 3 course meal was out of this world and beautifully presented and the staff were not only very polite and friendy but attentive and genuine. At the end of the meal the waiters brought mum out a celebration desert complete with candle, the waiter came up and told me very discreatly that the bill had been paid in full even though the voucher stated that there would be a 12.5% discretionary service charge which we would have been more than happy to pay. I can;t rate this place high enough l would give it a 20 star rating if l could. Thank you for making our visit so memorable"]}
