{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r433154697", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Vegetarian delight", "diner_date": " October 2016", "rating_date": "31 October 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Vidmante M", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r433154697-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Had a visit with my friend on Thursday night. Restaurant looked amazing the same as the views of river and canary wharf night scenery. We went for vegetarian tasting menu which was probably the best we ever had. Service was faultless and do not disturb too often, there were there when needed. Defenetly recommended for everyone with special occasion or romantic dinner. 10/10"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r429170759", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing treat", "diner_date": " September 2016", "rating_date": "18 October 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "lorenab103", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "12"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "8"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r429170759-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["My husband and I went for the tasting menu at the Peninsula as a treat for our anniversary. The food was delicious - not something you see on regular menus - and he went for the wine pairing option, so he also had the chance to try out 5 or 6 types of exquisite wine. The service was also impeccable (only popping up at the right moment so as not to interrupt, but full of insight on wine pairing and the food we were eating) and they never even mentioned the fact that we kept going on into the earlier hours (a bit past their closing time)."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r441398935", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "What a find ", "diner_date": " December 2016", "rating_date": "1 December 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "christine l", "reviewer_origin": ["Kent, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "310"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "123"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r441398935-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Decided to try the pre show menu before a concert at the O2. 3 courses including a glass of champagne for \u00a335. It was outstanding everything from the view the staff and the food was perfect. House wine at \u00a329 was delicious as was all the food. Hot smoked salmon and ham hock for starters and lamb and sea bream for main. Chocolate tart for pudding. Complimentary amuse bouche homemade bread and butter just added to the experience. As good as any fine dining restaurant in London. Can't wait to go back "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r441800774", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellent Food and Service", "diner_date": " November 2016", "rating_date": "3 December 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "198LindaD", "reviewer_origin": ["Poole, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "19"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "10"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r441800774-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["My husband and myself went for lunch at the Peninsula restaurant and had the tasting menu and pairing wine selection. It was absolutely amazing, tasted and presented really well. There was lots of food and wine and it was great to taste wine that should go with each course. The wine water (Ucha) was so knowledgeable and knew when to come to the table and when to leave us alone to chat. He even changed the wine when my husband didn't really like it that much and gave him a wine that he liked and complimented the dish.", "The food came at a nice pace and it meant that the whole experienced lasted a couple of hours, so it was an experience as well as just eating..", "I can't decide which was my favourite course as they were all so different and tasted wonderful - thank you to the amazing chefs for creating an amazing meal.", "The views are lovely over the Thames and there is plenty of space between tables.", "We have tasted some fantastic meals over the years in all different places all over the world but this has to be in the top 5. We will definitely be visiting you again when we come to London."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r457644012", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing ", "diner_date": " February 2017", "rating_date": "6 February 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Jagbir S", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r457644012-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I hardly ever write reviews but felt compelled to praise the staff and food at this restaurant. From the moment we walked in we were made to feel very special and the staff were extremely warm, friendly and informal. The food was delicious and in my opinion, to a Michelin standard. At the end they presented a birthday dessert which was the icing on the cake . Thank you for everything and to the hotel in general! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r458878644", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Definitely order the tasting menu!", "diner_date": " February 2017", "rating_date": "12 February 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Alahna K", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r458878644-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["The food was absolutely fantastic. We had 5 different dishes that were all paired with a different wine. There was a nice variety with our dishes and the ingredients. Another thing I enjoyed was how friendly and welcoming the staff were. Gabor and Eva really took care of us and were really funny. Perfect food and atmosphere!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r446551323", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Xmas Eve Taster Menu", "diner_date": " December 2016", "rating_date": "25 December 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Arnold L", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "171"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "92"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r446551323-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["1930 booking and arrived early and were seated at a window view table, restaurant was about half full if that nut quite atmospheric. We decided to have the taster Menu which was around 6/ 7courses with amusee bouch\u00e9e in between. The fish was beautifully cooked in a broth, Rabbit terrine was exceptional and the beef cooked medium rare to perfection. We did not take the wine flight simply because we felt it would be too much but I had a glass of super white recommended by the sommelier with the early courses and a lovely Spanish red again on recommendation with the beef. So food and drink was exceptional. Service was efficient, very friendly and unhurried. If anything the tasting menu was probably too much for us and we should have perhaps had the fixed 3 course but whatever this restaurant deserves to do well, the staff are great and knowledgeable and has great atmosphere. A really good location."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r427269906", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Beautiful", "diner_date": " October 2016", "rating_date": "12 October 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "GinKent", "reviewer_origin": ["Kent"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "73"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "45"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r427269906-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Lovely Restaurant with stunning views over the Thames. Food well presented and also very tasty. On the expensive side, but ok for a celebration"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d10148721", "id_comment": "g186338-d10148721-r391627521", "resto": "Peninsula_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d10148721-Reviews-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great place with an artist chef ", "diner_date": " July 2016", "rating_date": "12 July 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "saad098", "reviewer_origin": ["Riyadh, Saudi Arabia"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "30"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "13"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d10148721-r391627521-Peninsula_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["It was my wife's birthday and I selected the O2 intercontinental hotel to escape the centre of London.", "The restaurant with a great view on the thames and canary wharf with very friendly and professional staff.", "The food was great for eyes as well for the taste.", "I chose the Pyrenean milk fed lamb plate and it was perfect. My wife chose the vegetarian tasting menu and she really enjoyed it.", "I highly recommend the restaurant especially for the buisness meetings and special occasions away from the busy life of London's centre."]}
